OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781687892
OL,3,CYellow heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth East England
OL,6,FA yellow heat health alert has been
OL,7,Fissued for South East England as
OL,8,Ftemperatures are expected to rise over
OL,9,Fthe coming days.
OL,11,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,12,Fsaid the alert is currently in place
OL,13,Ffrom 3pm on Wednesday until 8pm on
OL,14,FMonday June 22.
OL,16,FThe agency said temperatures in the
OL,17,FSouth East could reach heatwave
OL,18,Fcriteria by the weekend, with the Met
OL,19,FOffice warning of 30C highs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
