FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781687892
OL,3,CYellow heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth East England
OL,6,FSimilar alerts have also been issued
OL,7,Ffor the East Midlands, the east of
OL,8,FEngland and London.
OL,10,FA UKHSA spokesperson said Friday is
OL,11,F"likely to see very warm, locally hot
OL,12,Fconditions", adding there will be a
OL,13,F"chance of a few thunderstorms".
OL,15,F"There is considerable uncertainty for
OL,16,Fthe duration of the very warm
OL,17,Fconditions however, as a weak weather
OL,18,Ffront moving east into Saturday may
OL,19,Fbring slightly lower temperatures and
OL,20,Ffresher conditions," they said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781687892
OL,3,CYellow heat health alert issued for
OL,4,CSouth East England
OL,6,F"However, there is the potential that
OL,7,Fthe weather front stalls toward the
OL,8,FSouth East allowing very warm or hot
OL,9,Fconditions to linger across, or near
OL,10,Fto the far south or South East,
OL,11,Fperhaps then becoming more extensive
OL,12,Fagain into the following week."
OL,14,FAccording to the UKHSA website, a
OL,15,Fyellow heat health alert means there
OL,16,Fis likely to be a "greater risk to
OL,17,Flife of vulnerable people" and an
OL,18,F"increased use of healthcare services"
OL,19,Fby this same demographic.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
